.TH SD300 1 "April 2026" "shaughvOS" "QubeTX 300 Series"
.SH NAME
sd300 \- QubeTX system diagnostics (SD-300)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B sd300
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B sd300
is the QubeTX SD-300 System Diagnostic. It provides a real-time
interactive TUI for system monitoring with nine sections covering
CPU, memory, disk, network, processes, and more.
.PP
The TUI updates continuously and is designed for quick triage of a
running machine without leaving the terminal.
.SH OPTIONS
See
.B sd300 \-\-help
for the full list of flags and modes.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR shaughvos (1),
.BR tr300 (1),
.BR nd300 (1),
.BR speedqx (1)
